        <updateDate>2021-05-04T14:38:51Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill prohibits the attachment of a 2021 recovery rebate by legal process, including assignment, levy, or garnishment. A <i>2021 recovery rebate</i> is a stimulus payment provided by the American Rescue Plan of 2021 for individual taxpayers and their dependents who have been affected by the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
